    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and accepted given that ASTM F1717 mandates a single load configuration and the remaining evidence base robustly supports the compression-bending prediction claim. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the 510(k) submission decision. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; the digital signature workflow is pending organizational PKI provisioning and will be applied prior to archival submission.",
